code: @Override public FD load(LeafReaderContext context) {     if (context.reader().getFieldInfos().fieldInfo(fieldName) == null) {         // The next time the field is found, we do cache.         return empty(context.reader().maxDoc()).     }     try {         FD fd = cache.load(context, this).         return fd.     } catch (Exception e) {         if (e instanceof ElasticsearchException) {             throw (ElasticsearchException) e.         } else {             throw new ElasticsearchException(e).         }     } }
